name: Ho-Oh
Attack1Text: This attack does 50 damage to 1 of your opponent's Pokemon. (Don't apply Weakness and Resistance for Benched Pokemon.)
Attack2Text: Discard an Energy from this Pokemon.

name: Reshiram
Attack1Text: This attack does 20 damage to each of your opponent's Benched Pokemon. (Don't apply Weakness and Resistance for Benched Pokemon.)
Attack2Text: If Zekrom is on your Bench, this attack does 80 more damage.

name: Kyogre
Attack1Text: Discard the top 5 cards of your deck, and then choose 2 of your opponent's Benched Pokemon. This attack does 50 damage for each Energy card you discarded in this way to each of those Pokemon. (Don't apply Weakness and Resistance for Benched Pokemon.)

name: Palkia
AbilityText: As long as this Pokemon is in the Active Spot, your opponent can't play any Stadium cards from their hand.
Attack1Text: During your next turn, this Pokemon's Overdrive Smash attack does 80 more damage (before applying Weakness and Resistance).

name: Pikachu
Attack2Text: Flip a coin. If tails, this Pokemon also does 10 damage to itself.

name: Zekrom
Attack1Text: If your opponent has a Stadium in play, discard it.
Attack2Text: If Reshiram is on your Bench, this attack does 80 more damage.

name: Mew
AbilityText: Once during your turn, if this Pokemon is in the Active Spot, you may look at the top 6 cards of your deck, reveal an Item card you find there, and put it into your hand. Shuffle the other cards back into your deck.

name: Xerneas
Attack1Text: Search your deck for up to 3 basic Energy cards of different types and attach them to your Pokemon in any way you like. Then, shuffle your deck.

name: Cosmog
Attack1Text: Flip a coin. If heads, during your opponent's next turn, prevent all damage done to this Pokemon by attacks.

name: Cosmoem
Attack1Text: Flip a coin. If heads, during your opponent's next turn, prevent all damage done to this Pokemon by attacks.

name: Lunala
Attack1Text: Double the number of damage counters on each of your opponent's Pokemon.
Attack2Text: This attack also does 30 damage to 1 of your opponent's Benched Pokemon. (Don't apply Weakness and Resistance for Benched Pokemon.)

name: Groudon
Attack1Text: Discard the top 5 cards of your deck. This attack does 80 damage for each Energy card you discarded in this way.

name: Yveltal
Attack1Text: Discard up to 3 Special Energy from your opponent's Pokemon.

name: Dialga
Attack1Text: Put a card from your discard pile into your hand.
Attack2Text: This attack does 20 more damage for each Metal Energy attached to this Pokemon.

name: Solgaleo
AbilityText: Once during your turn, if this Pokemon is on your Bench, you may switch it with your Active Pokemon.
Attack1Text: Attach up to 2 basic Energy cards from your discard pile to 1 of your Benched Pokemon.

name: Lugia
Attack1Text: This attack does 20 damage for each Energy attached to both Active Pokemon.
Attack2Text: During your next turn, this Pokemon can't attack.

name: Mew
AbilityText: Once during your turn, if this Pokemon is in the Active Spot, you may look at the top 6 cards of your deck, reveal an Item card you find there, and put it into your hand. Shuffle the other cards back into your deck.
